-- MOVES-RBC unit names Kerry Hugh-Jones institutional portfolio manager
-- 
-- Thu Sep 04, 2014 06:39AM EDT
-- None



Sept 4 (Reuters) - BlueBay Asset Management LLP, part of Royal Bank of Canada's <RY.TO> asset management business, said it appointed Kerry Hugh-Jones as institutional portfolio manager.

Hugh-Jones, who was previously head of business development at Eclectica Asset Management, will work with the global leveraged finance team, BlueBay said.